    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>职位招聘：需要雇佣兵。货到付款。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入，雇佣兵！我们公司的座右铭很简单：货物必达<strong>。 </strong>维修随便。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有人知道原因，但数十年前的这场灾变让大西洋彻底干涸，留下一片环境恶劣的荒芜之地。如今，那里爬满了巨大的虫子，充斥着复苏的远古武器和各种古怪的变异生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至于你的任务？就是用火车护送客户的珍贵货物，穿越这片险恶的地带。你将在每一站抵挡敌人无尽的攻击。 如果抵达时货物完好无损，就算胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《都是澳洲惹的祸》并不拘泥于已有游戏类型……而是自成一派。踏入战术反向弹幕地狱，见证深谋远虑的回合制塔防与独特单位合并机制的巧妙融合，并通过轰天震地、令人血脉偾张的铁轨反向弹幕地狱战斗来增强体验。运筹帷幄，抵御源源不断涌现的敌人，然后化身弹幕地狱，释放超载武器，在混战中横扫千军。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>工作职责：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396130/extras/e65cf42fe7217c5c95f549e6bdcb43a8.poster.avif?t=1771943174\" width=616 height=352 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396130/extras/e65cf42fe7217c5c95f549e6bdcb43a8.webm?t=1771943174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>守护你的车站：</strong>在列车出发前，对有限的单位进行战略部署，抵挡不断涌来的敌人。战斗如同下棋，但速度更快，任何错误都有可能造成惊天一炸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396130/extras/547f448a209041b103a13d9de79b087f.poster.avif?t=1771943174\" width=616 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396130/extras/547f448a209041b103a13d9de79b087f.webm?t=1771943174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进化你的单位：</strong>即时合并单位，解锁30多种单位组成的1500多种搭配。创造强到离谱的全新单位或专业队伍。多进行尝试是关键……但小心别把自己炸飞了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396130/extras/c2d93ecb15af9579fba52dac2c440780.poster.avif?t=1771943174\" width=616 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396130/extras/c2d93ecb15af9579fba52dac2c440780.webm?t=1771943174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在反向弹幕地狱中生存：</strong>列车启动，混乱伊始。你将化身弹幕地狱，展开紧张刺激的铁轨战斗，使用超载武器，横扫千军。记住，货物必须完整送达。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396130/extras/75c62867c9d07eb278549d043dfba28c.poster.avif?t=1771943174\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396130/extras/75c62867c9d07eb278549d043dfba28c.webm?t=1771943174\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自定义你的策略：</strong>每次成功守护车站后，挑选特殊奖励卡以获得独特效果与加成。将卡片与不断升级的队伍进行搭配，制定创新策略，打造独具一格的战斗配置。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速规划的战术塔防</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >反向弹幕地狱战斗，进攻才能确保生存</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特合并机制，超过1500种单位组合和30多种单位类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过奖励卡实现深度自定义对局</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可解锁大量带有独特属性的列车模型</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>感兴趣吗？立刻申请</strong>——名额每日随机开放。训练自便。无需长期承诺。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>现在添加至愿望单，以便在第一时间获得征召。</strong></h2>",
